08:18.225 --> 08:19.306
We would capture it electronically.

08:19.326 --> 08:20.867
What we are preserving is the content.

08:21.308 --> 08:21.708
That's right.

08:21.828 --> 08:23.750
You're preserving the content, not the artifact.

08:23.770 --> 08:25.892
And shedding the artifact, so to speak?

08:26.233 --> 08:26.513
Indeed.

08:26.773 --> 08:27.013
Indeed.

08:27.053 --> 08:27.994
