23:00.760 --> 23:04.744
We do not have any good management models thus far.

23:05.625 --> 23:07.307
Man, the field's changing too fast.

23:07.327 --> 23:07.427
Yeah.

23:07.947 --> 23:19.479
How about, you know, the integrity of the—I mean, it's known, and you see some gorgeous fifteenth-century books that, you know, they've lasted quite well over five hundred years.

23:19.499 --> 23:26.886
We know really, basically, how long paper lasts, and if you control the environment, it'll last longer.

23:27.288 --> 23:28.349
Sure.

23:29.130 --> 23:33.455
